FT  07 MAR 94 / International Company News: Improvement at Lend Lease
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
   By NIKKI TAIT
</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>
   SYDNEY
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
Lend Lease, the large Sydney-based property and financial services group,
reported net operating profit of ADollars 118.9m (USDollars 85m) for the six
months to end-December, up 7 per cent on the year-ago figure, writes Nikki
Tait in Sydney.
The increase was held back by a doubled tax charge. At the pre-tax level
there was a 17 per cent rise, to ADollars 144.5m.
