FT  07 MAR 94 / Observer: Fair winds
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Bo Goranson is a businessman hoping to prove that running a yacht isn't
necessarily an expensive hobby.
His Intrum Justitia debt collection group is sponsoring a yacht in the
Whitbread round-the-world race, which started last September. The company
